{"tid":2118716,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"淡化中企色彩戰略？抖音宣布未來3年在美招聘1萬員工","createTime":"2020-07-21T15:34:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-23T00:51:39.000Z","uid":141151,"like":4,"dislike":50,"uniUserReply":42,"replies":[{"pid":"d926e3de315e285cb9012b1da373892ba9f43d12","tid":2118716,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T15:34:53.000Z","msg":"淡化中企色彩戰略？抖音宣布未來3年在美招聘1萬員工<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3235516\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3235516&d=PhzZiar3PrZ%2B4r6hY23Rj2bkIIQgOyZVEIOEDwMYbAQ%3D&h=66f4373c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3235516&h=53d8b9af\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3235516</a><br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕美國眾議院於當地時間20日通過《國防授權法》修正案，禁止聯邦政府雇員以及國會所有議員的公務機使用中國影音平台抖音海外版「TikTok」。面對此一打擊，TikTok於今（21）日宣布，計畫在3年內於美國增加約1萬名員工。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"red\">綜合外媒報導，TikTok母公司字節跳動本週稍早取消了與英國官員的談判。該公司原本打算於倫敦設立總部，並於當地招募3000名職員，但談判破裂無疾而終。如今再受到美國眾議院一記重拳，公司連忙宣布未來3年內會雇用10000名當地員工。TikTok現下在美國有約1400名職員，而今年1月時人數還不到500名。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n僅管TikTok一再否認收集用戶個資，然而韓國通訊委員會（KCC）於7月15日才表示，因TikTok未經家長同意，便收集6000份14歲以下兒童的數據，因此對TikTok罰款1.86億韓元（約合新台幣458萬元）。"},{"pid":"577d85217d265f27f37b25edb1b3ab5aec511a30","tid":2118716,"uid":42767,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T15:35:47.000Z","msg":"罰太少"},{"pid":"1a816d7a5048440c7fb3174e0ad101abd0bb7735","tid":2118716,"uid":179729,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T15:36:31.000Z","msg":"下一個就係微信<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3b5b2a7035a4d20000fb695f5339eb9e6e972b0","tid":2118716,"uid":67065,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T15:37:09.000Z","msg":"請1萬個間碟???"}